Heat oven to 350 degrees F. Beat cream cheese, sour cream and dressing mix with mixer until blended. Add broccoli and 1-1/2 cups Cheddar cheese; mix well. Spread into 9-inch pie plate. Bake 20 minutes. Sprinkle with remaining Cheddar cheese; bake 5 minutes or until melted. Serve with NABISCO Crackers.